                <h1>Writer and activist Dave  Eggers to give lecture at Duke</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/eddf0f53-32fc-4e12-a2a5-8bfa11dce199.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="" class="w-100">
